Linux wxPHP Shell
========================================================================

On this directory you will find a script to launch a terminal with
a message telling the user how to launch wxphp scripts. This
scripts can be packaged and used to add an application menu entry
for wxPHP.

========================================================================
launcher.sh:
========================================================================

Verifies the current system for a valid terminal emulator and
launches it.

========================================================================
shell.sh:
========================================================================

Executed by launcher.sh this file outputs shell_header.txt and executes
/bin/bash so the user can start processing commands.
